# TeleVU

Medical Imaging Server; PACS, that gives patient total control over medical images
Televu can be deployed stand alone, or as a router in exising systems, to replace normal patient IDs with cheqd DIDs
System is being developed to compliant with relevant standards;
IHE, HL7, DICOM, HIPAA

Typical Scenario

- RIS Simulator Send Order Messages; HL7 ORM^O01 messages with patient DIDs
- PACS System recieves Order, and prepares Modality Worklist entries for Radiology machines to get patient information and write inside DICOM images and studies
- patient grants access by issuing VC for Doctors DID
Machine Queries PACS, gets patient Info, Construct DICOM Medical Image, and send to PACS
Doctor, Using DICOM Viewer from his workstation, queries PACS for patietns images
-PACS filter results by verifying VCs issued by Patients to Doctors


## RUN

docker compose up

cd test/scripts
./test.sh

#RUN dicom viewer with AET as doctor named Charles or Dave
